<section id="1001A_S000V" variety="S000V">
<name>LIGHTING</name>
<ttl id="1001A_S000V_7AVRC_T00AG" variety="T00AG">
<name>SIDE TURN SIGNAL LIGHT ASSEMBLY (for Outer Rear View Mirror)</name>
<para id="RM0000015DT03HX" category="A" type-id="30014" name-id="LE4AV-02" from="201202">
<name>INSTALLATION</name>
<subpara id="RM0000015DT03HX_02" type-id="11" category="10" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00004X000000">
<content3 releasenbr="1">
<atten4>
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>Use the same procedure for the RH and LH sides.</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>The procedure listed below is for the LH side.</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</atten4>
</content3>
</subpara>
<subpara id="RM0000015DT03HX_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM0000015DT03HX_01_0009" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00004WW00000">
<ptxt>INSTALL SIDE TURN SIGNAL LIGHT ASSEMBLY LH</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Connect the connector.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Install the side turn signal light assembly LH with the 2 screws.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM0000015DT03HX_01_0013" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000046300000">
<ptxt>INSTALL OUTER MIRROR COVER LH
</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Attach the 2 claws as shown in the illustration.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="B280815" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="B280813" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>Attach the 6 claws to install the mirror cover LH.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="B278385" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>After installing the outer mirror cover, check that there is no gap between the cover and mirror body.</ptxt>
<atten4>
<ptxt>If there is a gap between the cover and body, noise will occur during driving.</ptxt>
</atten4>
</s2>
<s2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="B278444E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>Using a T25 "TORX" socket wrench, install the screws.</ptxt>
<torque>
<torqueitem>
<t-value1>3.3</t-value1>
<t-value2>34</t-value2>
<t-value3>30</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
<atten4>
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>Clean the threads of the screw with non-residue solvent.</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Apply adhesive to the threads of the screw.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Adhesive</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>Toyota Genuine Adhesive 1324, Three Bond 1324 or equivalent</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
</item>
</list1>
</atten4>
<table>
<title>Text in Illustration</title>
<tgroup cols="2">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="0.41in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="3.72in"/>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>*1</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>Adhesive</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Attach the 5 claws.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Install the rubber base with the screw.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="B278446E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>Apply new tape as shown in the illustration.</ptxt>
<table>
<title>Text in Illustration</title>
<tgroup cols="2">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="0.41in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="3.72in"/>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>*1</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>Tape</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>*a</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>40 mm (1.58 in.)</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</s2>
</content1></s-1>
<s-1 id="RM0000015DT03HX_01_0014" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000045U00000">
<ptxt>INSTALL OUTER MIRROR LH
</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="B278388" width="2.775699831in" height="2.775699831in"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>Attach the 2 claws as shown in the illustration.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="B285970" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>Attach the 2 claws to install the outer mirror LH.</ptxt>
<atten3>
<ptxt>Do not push in the glass with excessive force. Doing so may break the mirror surface.</ptxt>
</atten3>
</s2>
</content1></s-1>
<s-1 id="RM0000015DT03HX_01_0012" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00004WX00000">
<ptxt>INSTALL OUTER REAR VIEW MIRROR ASSEMBLY LH</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<ptxt>(See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM0000015DT03AX"/>).</ptxt>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
